    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The Oath of Conquest calls to paladins who seek glory in battle and the subjugation of their enemies. It isn’t enough for these paladins to establish order. They must crush the forces of chaos. Sometimes called knight tyrants or iron mongers, those who swear this oath gather into grim orders that serve gods or philosophies of war and well-ordered might.</p>\n<p>Some of these paladins go so far as to consort with the powers of the Nine Hells, valuing the rule of law over the balm of mercy. The archdevil Bel, warlord of Avernus, counts many of these paladins – called hell knights – as his most ardent supporters. Hell knights cover their armor with trophies taken from fallen enemies, a grim warning to any who dare oppose them and the decrees of their lords. These knights are often most fiercely resisted by other paladins of this oath, who believe that the hell knights have wandered too far into darkness.</p>\n<h3>Oath of Conquest Spells</h3>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<td>Paladin Level</td>\n<td>Spells</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.g2B1luNF1dvQGWgA]{Armor of Agathys}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.UFyMGkLPBAGvdsvO]{Command}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.NXOXaNWD6HazQkmY]{Hold Person}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.hpIDXvgdhqbiXmHT]{Spiritual Weapon}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.TDOF2hmjvfcM1ZZS]{Bestow Curse}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.Lg5snaPweDbWUmTL]{Fear}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>13th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.mmmnJAeXZ4TaxPwy]{Dominate Beast}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.BmWgCc1hVRkNlQHf]{Stoneskin}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>17th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.pgfEb63k38KiSHoh]{Cloudkill}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.vZVDWUj69cLI1Qhz]{Dominate Person}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3>Oath of Conquest Features</h3>\n<p>3rd: @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.jkvXwlabeFDzqFsb]{Tenets of Conquest}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.Vbn2Uh7yKfNwNsLi]{Conquering Presence}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.YsJjwQrgqJNlSzeN]{Guided Strike}</p>\n<p>7th: @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.6dMldTjqxwUPpLMi]{Aura of Conquest}</p>\n<p>15th: @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.3CtdZAjtWZSK6Wed]{Scornful Rebuke}</p>\n<p>20th: @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.D1VX682yEsH7K28D]{Invincible Conqueror}</p>",
